data.description:
Welcome to Emerald Coast Marine Group
Northwest Florida’s Premier, All-Inclusive Marine Experience!
Emerald Coast Marine Group is very pleased to offer two convenient locations to serve the needs of our valued area boaters.

Our headquarters location in the Niceville/Destin, FL market is nestled on the north side of the Choctawhatchee Bay. It features a full-service marine center including a newly constructed dry stack storage facility, marina with wet slips, plus new and premium pre-owned boat sales, yacht and brokerage division, parts and service department, yacht club, boat club, and waterfront restaurant and bar.

Our newest sales location in Orange Beach, AL is situated at The Wharf in a 6000-square foot facility with inviting tropical, open-air showroom featuring a display of new and premium owned boats, along with brokerage and consignment units.

Emerald Coast Marine Group is locally-owned and operated by boating enthusiasts dedicated to delivering the ultimate, all-inclusive marine experience! As our earned Five-Star customer rating attests, each member of the Emerald Coast Marine Team reflects and embodies an unprecedented commitment to our customers.  We invite you to tour both of our facilities, experience our genuine Southern hospitality and meet the members of our team. Come discover why we believe … Life is Better with a Boat!
